source.name: Annual Survey of Public-Employee Retirement Systems (State-Administered Pensions)
source.description: The Annual Survey of Public-Employee Retirement Systems (State-Administered Pensions) provides revenues, expenditures, financial assets, liabilities  and membership information for defined benefit public employee retirement systems. Data are shown by state, for the state-administered systems. There are 222 state-administered public employee retirement systems.
